profile:
Studio Linea is an Oakville-based company providing professional home staging and redesigning services to homeowners, realtors and home builders.
Studio Linea is a certified, registered home stagers company with the Real Estate Staging Association. It offers a dynamic and competitive edge to the art of home-staging.We offer professional services dedicated to assist homeowners in preparing their house for sale during this delicate time. Our commitment and passion to any project, small or large scale, has always been recognized by referrals and recommendations.

profile:
Our Clients are #1 priority so we truly believe in high business ethics as far as relations with our clients are concerned. We strongly intend to develop a closer trust based on a long-term business relationship with our clients. Equally important to us is that our quality of products delivered matches the quality of our service. Our furniture is well maintained and spotless. If an item in our collection is damaged, ripped, broken or stained… it does NOT leave our showroom.
When you team up with Stagers Choice, you get more than a catalog of fine furniture, you get a team of professionals willing to go beyond to help you with your project and make your experience with us efficient & profitable.

We have flexible prices & lease terms and delivery all over GTA is available within 24 hours.

profile:
Natural Look Staging has been in business for 12 years.

We specialize in staging properties.  If  there is a property for country, confection or modern needed we can accommodate this.

We are able to stage any room in a house.  Supply of leather sofas, glass dining room tables as well as beds with frames.  Pictures and props are used to fill the spots to catch the buyers eyes.



Every house needs to be staged differently as each house is different.   Staging  needs to fit the characteristics of the house.  

The items used for staging are also available to purchase.  

We have an overwhelming amount of clients calling back for more services,  as well as giving us referrals to their family and friends.

The rent for the furniture is based on a monthly fee.

The staging fee is a one time fee.

The rental fee covers everything put in the house for a flat fee.

Staged properties  is essential for selling your property quickly and for more.  You want your house staged property so the buyers go inside with a easy welcoming flow.

Call us and see what we can do for you.

profile:
Home Staging is a must have marketing tool for selling a home. Without it, your property can sit on the market longer, ultimately selling for less money.

At Scene Stealers, our priority is to make a showstopping first impression for potential buyers. Our goal is to create an emotional connection. Let us help you showcase your space — make it a true scene stealer that will sell faster and fetch top dollar.

We will help you invest in the right areas of your home for the best return on your investment. We showcase the selling features while minimizing the less desirables. During a consultation, we will walk you through each step of the process. Scene Stealers will develop a plan that is specific to you, your timeline and your budget.

Services Provided
Art Selection, Decluttering, Furniture Selection, Holiday Decorating, Home Staging
